is from correction and grounding both in reusable, modular components, our approach enables continuous improvement through incremental updates to either the verifier suite or the correction memory bank. Potential impact includes deployment in real-world summarization pipelines (e.g., news aggregation, scientific digesting) where reliability and plug-and-play integration are paramount.",
